Build instructions
==================

WARNING: This pre-release version of LucED is experimental and might not
work as expected.

Requirements: The external libs libpcre und liblua are needed, see
   
   * http://www.pcre.org/
   * http://lua.org/
   
Try the following commands for building LucED:

   cd editor
   touch sandbox.mk
   touch sandbox_options.h
   make
   
See the file "Makefile" for possible adjustments for the "sandbox.mk" file and the
file "options.h" for possible defines for the "sandbox_options.h" file.

